data.description: Lovely 3 Bedroom 2 Bath home on a 0.75 acre cul de sac lot. This wonderful ranch style home has been well taken care of with fresh paint and new carpet it is move in ready. The kitchen is open to the living room with vaulted ceilings.  The master bedroom has a trey ceiling, master bath features a garden tub with separate shower and double vanities. Two car garage.  This home is conveniently located approximately 2 miles to I-85, less than 10 miles to Tanger Outlets, 30 minutes to Athens, Gainesville, Habersham and Buford.  Call now for your appointment.  Can qualify with USDA, VA, FHA down payment assistance, conventional loan 1% down payment assistance income limit qualifying.  Seller willing to pay up to $7000 towards closing costs with acceptable contract.  All of this available with preferred local lender.
